<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8"/>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
<title>Kalshi BTC Strategy Backtest</title>
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/Chart.js/4.4.1/chart.umd.min.js"></script>
<style>
  :root {
    --bg: #0d1117; --surface: #161b22; --surface2: #21262d;
    --border: #30363d; --text: #e6edf3; --muted: #8b949e;
    --green: #3fb950; --red: #f85149; --blue: #58a6ff;
    --gold: #d29922; --purple: #bc8cff;
  }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  body { background: var(--bg); color: var(--text); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; font-size: 14px; }
  
  .header { padding: 20px 24px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; }
  .header h1 { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600; }
  .header .sub { color: var(--muted); font-size: 13px; margin-top: 2px; }
  .badge { background: var(--surface2); border: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 3px 8px; border-radius: 12px; font-size: 12px; color: var(--muted); }
  
  .tabs { display: flex; gap: 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 0 24px; }
  .tab-btn { background: none; border: none; color: var(--muted); padding: 12px 16px; cursor: pointer; font-size: 13px; border-bottom: 2px solid transparent; transition: all 0.2s; }
  .tab-btn:hover { color: var(--text); }
  .tab-btn.active { color: var(--blue); border-bottom-color: var(--blue); }
  
  .tab-content { display: none; }
  .tab-content.active { display: block; }
  
  .page { padding: 24px; }
  
  /* Period selector */
  .period-bar { display: flex; gap: 8px; margin-bottom: 20px; align-items: center; }
  .period-btn { background: var(--surface2); border: 1px solid var(--border); color: var(--muted); padding: 6px 14px; border-radius: 6px; cursor: pointer; font-size: 13px; transition: all 0.2s; }
  .period-btn.active { background: var(--blue); border-color: var(--blue); color: #fff; }
  .period-label { color: var(--muted); font-size: 12px; margin-right: 4px; }
  
  /* Stat cards */
  .cards { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(180px, 1fr)); gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .card { background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 8px; padding: 16px; }
  .card-label { color: var(--muted); font-size: 11px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .card-value { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 600; }
  .card-sub { color: var(--muted); font-size: 12px; margin-top: 4px; }
  .green { color: var(--green); }
  .red { color: var(--red); }
  .blue { color: var(--blue); }
  .gold { color: var(--gold); }
  .purple { color: var(--purple); }
  
  /* Chart containers */
  .chart-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr; gap: 16px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .chart-box { background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 8px; padding: 16px; }
  .chart-box h3 { font-size: 13px; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 12px; font-weight: 500; }
  .chart-box canvas { max-height: 260px; }
  
  .chart-full { background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 8px; padding: 16px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .chart-full h3 { font-size: 13px; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 12px; font-weight: 500; }
  .chart-full canvas { max-height: 300px; }
  
  /* Mode overview */
  .mode-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .mode-card { background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 8px; padding: 16px; cursor: pointer; transition: border-color 0.2s; }
  .mode-card:hover { border-color: var(--blue); }
  .mode-card.active { border-color: var(--blue); background: rgba(88,166,255,0.05); }
  .mode-card h3 { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .mode-stats { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 4px; }
  .mode-stat { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; font-size: 12px; }
  .mode-stat span:first-child { color: var(--muted); }
  
  .wr-bar { height: 6px; border-radius: 3px; background: var(--surface2); margin-top: 8px; overflow: hidden; }
  .wr-fill { height: 100%; border-radius: 3px; transition: width 0.5s; }
  
  /* Tables */
  .table-box { background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; }
  .table-box h3 { padding: 12px 16px; font-size: 13px; color: var(--muted); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); font-weight: 500; }
  .table-wrap { overflow-x: auto; max-height: 340px; overflow-y: auto; }
  table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; }
  th { background: var(--surface2); color: var(--muted); font-size: 11px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px; padding: 8px 12px; text-align: left; position: sticky; top: 0; }
  td { padding: 7px 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); font-size: 12px; }
  tr:hover td { background: var(--surface2); }
  .win-row td { }
  .loss-row td { background: rgba(248,81,73,0.04); }
  .pill { display: inline-block; padding: 1px 8px; border-radius: 10px; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; }
  .pill-win { background: rgba(63,185,80,0.15); color: var(--green); }
  .pill-loss { background: rgba(248,81,73,0.15); color: var(--red); }
  .pill-yes { background: rgba(88,166,255,0.15); color: var(--blue); }
  .pill-no { background: rgba(188,140,255,0.15); color: var(--purple); }
  
  /* Summary compare table */
  .compare-table { background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .compare-table table { width: 100%; }
  .compare-table th, .compare-table td { padding: 10px 14px; text-align: right; }
  .compare-table th:first-child, .compare-table td:first-child { text-align: left; }
  .compare-table thead th { background: var(--surface2); font-size: 11px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--muted); }
  
  /* Loss analysis */
  .loss-detail { background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 8px; padding: 16px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .loss-detail h3 { font-size: 13px; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .loss-item { background: rgba(248,81,73,0.06); border: 1px solid rgba(248,81,73,0.2); border-radius: 6px; padding: 10px 14px; margin-bottom: 8px; font-size: 12px; }
  .loss-item strong { color: var(--red); }
  
  .footnote { color: var(--muted); font-size: 11px; padding: 8px 0; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); margin-top: 20px; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="header">
  <div>
    <h1>📊 Kalshi BTC Strategy Backtest</h1>
    <div class="sub">Historical simulation on real Binance 1-min OHLCV data &nbsp;·&nbsp; BTC/USDT 15-min windows</div>
  </div>
  <span class="badge" id="genAt"></span>
</div>

<div class="tabs">
  <button class="tab-btn active" onclick="switchTab('overview')">Overview</button>
  <button class="tab-btn" onclick="switchTab('mode1')">Mode 1 — Early Entry</button>
  <button class="tab-btn" onclick="switchTab('mode2')">Mode 2 — Distance Play</button>
  <button class="tab-btn" onclick="switchTab('mode3')">Mode 3 — Contrarian</button>
</div>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════ OVERVIEW ════════════════════════════════ -->
<div id="tab-overview" class="tab-content active">
<div class="page">

  <div class="period-bar">
    <span class="period-label">Period:</span>
    <button class="period-btn active" onclick="setPeriod('days90',this)">90 Days</button>
    <button class="period-btn" onclick="setPeriod('days30',this)">30 Days</button>
    <button class="period-btn" onclick="setPeriod('days10',this)">10 Days</button>
  </div>

  <!-- Mode cards -->
  <div class="mode-grid" id="overview-cards"></div>

  <!-- Summary compare table -->
  <div class="compare-table">
    <table id="compare-tbl">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Strategy</th>
          <th>Period</th>
          <th>Trades</th>
          <th>Win Rate</th>
          <th>Start</th>
          <th>End</th>
          <th>Net P&L</th>
          <th>ROI</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody id="compare-tbody"></tbody>
    </table>
  </div>

  <!-- Combined equity chart -->
  <div class="chart-full">
    <h3>Equity Curve Comparison (all 3 modes, selected period)</h3>
    <canvas id="equity-compare-chart"></canvas>
  </div>

  <!-- Win rate bar chart -->
  <div class="chart-grid">
    <div class="chart-box">
      <h3>Win Rate by Mode &amp; Period</h3>
      <canvas id="winrate-chart"></canvas>
    </div>
    <div class="chart-box">
      <h3>Trade Count by Mode &amp; Period</h3>
      <canvas id="trades-chart"></canvas>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>
</div>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════ MODE 1 ════════════════════════════════ -->
<div id="tab-mode1" class="tab-content">
<div class="page">
  <div class="period-bar">
    <span class="period-label">Period:</span>
    <button class="period-btn active" onclick="setModePeriod('m1','days90',this)">90 Days</button>
    <button class="period-btn" onclick="setModePeriod('m1','days30',this)">30 Days</button>
    <button class="period-btn" onclick="setModePeriod('m1','days10',this)">10 Days</button>
  </div>
  <div class="cards" id="m1-cards"></div>
  <div class="chart-full">
    <h3>Bankroll History — Mode 1 (Kelly Sizing, 50¢ contracts)</h3>
    <canvas id="m1-equity-chart"></canvas>
  </div>
  <div class="chart-grid">
    <div class="chart-box">
      <h3>Daily P&L Distribution</h3>
      <canvas id="m1-pnl-chart"></canvas>
    </div>
    <div class="chart-box">
      <h3>Confidence vs Win Rate</h3>
      <canvas id="m1-conf-chart"></canvas>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="table-box">
    <h3>Trade History (most recent 50)</h3>
    <div class="table-wrap">
      <table>
        <thead><tr><th>#</th><th>Date UTC</th><th>Side</th><th>Confidence</th><th>Strike</th><th>BTC Entry</th><th>Settlement</th><th>Bet</th><th>P&L</th><th>Bankroll</th><th>Result</th></tr></thead>
        <tbody id="m1-trade-table"></tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="footnote">Mode 1 logic: Enters in first 0-2 minutes of a 15-min window. Bull score 0-100 from RSI, candle streak, volume spike, and distance. Requires 70%+ confidence. Half-Kelly position sizing capped at 5% of bankroll. Assumed entry price: 50¢ (even money).</div>
</div>
</div>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════ MODE 2 ════════════════════════════════ -->
<div id="tab-mode2" class="tab-content">
<div class="page">
  <div class="period-bar">
    <span class="period-label">Period:</span>
    <button class="period-btn active" onclick="setModePeriod('m2','days90',this)">90 Days</button>
    <button class="period-btn" onclick="setModePeriod('m2','days30',this)">30 Days</button>
    <button class="period-btn" onclick="setModePeriod('m2','days10',this)">10 Days</button>
  </div>
  <div class="cards" id="m2-cards"></div>
  <div class="chart-full">
    <h3>Bankroll History — Mode 2 (3% flat bet, distance-scaled odds)</h3>
    <canvas id="m2-equity-chart"></canvas>
  </div>
  <div class="chart-grid">
    <div class="chart-box">
      <h3>Win Rate by Distance Bucket</h3>
      <canvas id="m2-dist-chart"></canvas>
    </div>
    <div class="chart-box">
      <h3>P&L per Trade</h3>
      <canvas id="m2-pnl-chart"></canvas>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="loss-detail" id="m2-losses"></div>
  <div class="table-box">
    <h3>All Trades</h3>
    <div class="table-wrap">
      <table>
        <thead><tr><th>#</th><th>Date UTC</th><th>Side</th><th>Strike</th><th>BTC Entry</th><th>Distance</th><th>Odds</th><th>Bet</th><th>Settlement</th><th>P&L</th><th>Bankroll</th><th>Result</th></tr></thead>
        <tbody id="m2-trade-table"></tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="footnote">Mode 2 logic: Enters at minutes 5-7. Requires $200+ distance from strike. Filters out overbought/oversold RSI, and 3-candle momentum against the position. Contract odds: $200-399 dist = 70¢, $400-599 = 78¢, $600+ = 85¢. Bet size = 3% of bankroll.</div>
</div>
</div>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════ MODE 3 ════════════════════════════════ -->
<div id="tab-mode3" class="tab-content">
<div class="page">
  <div class="period-bar">
    <span class="period-label">Period:</span>
    <button class="period-btn active" onclick="setModePeriod('m3','days90',this)">90 Days</button>
    <button class="period-btn" onclick="setModePeriod('m3','days30',this)">30 Days</button>
    <button class="period-btn" onclick="setModePeriod('m3','days10',this)">10 Days</button>
  </div>
  <div class="cards" id="m3-cards"></div>
  <div class="chart-full">
    <h3>Cumulative Paper P&L — Mode 3 ($1 flat bets, paper only)</h3>
    <canvas id="m3-pnl-chart"></canvas>
  </div>
  <div class="table-box">
    <h3>Recent Trades (last 50)</h3>
    <div class="table-wrap">
      <table>
        <thead><tr><th>#</th><th>Date UTC</th><th>Side</th><th>Strike</th><th>Settlement</th><th>P&L</th><th>Result</th></tr></thead>
        <tbody id="m3-trade-table"></tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="footnote">Mode 3 logic: Contrarian lottery. Fires when first 2 candles of a window show a strong directional move (≥0.08%). Bets against the momentum at 10¢ contracts. $1 flat bet, paper only — never real money. High volume, low win rate, but positive expected value at 10¢.</div>
</div>
</div>

